    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained to ensure a reliable driving experience. The engine starts up easily and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides steady and predictable shifting. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the exterior retains a solid finish with just a few small blemishes typical for its age. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
