    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a nice luster, though you will notice some minor surface scratches and a few small door dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and well-kept, showing only moderate wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffs on the plastic trim. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for daily driving, offering a dependable option for its next owner.",
