    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a motorcar of uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection. Meticulously preserved and free of any discernible wear, it stands as a testament to rigorous maintenance and superior care. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
